longBusinessSummary: Immage Biotherapeutics Corp. does not have significant business operations. Previously, it was engaged in developing novel immunotherapy biologics to treat various cancers in the United States. The company was formerly known as Epicure Charcoal, Inc. and changed its name to Immage Biotherapeutics Corp. in June 2015. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Bethesda, Maryland. Immage Biotherapeutics Corp. is a subsidiary of Coventry International Limited.
